00C: I'm not in charge of the Chivitrons, but i can talk to your 
characters until something else happens. =)

--- Axis / Lokk ---

  Lokk picks up the noise on the exterior speakers, and sits 
up, "Hey Axis we've got visitors.
  Axis jumps to his feet, having zoned out. "Alright, we'd better 
talk to them." He pauses, "Uhh, where are the others?"
  "No clue," replies Lokk as he leaps to his feet and out the side 
of tha hatch. Axis is close behind him.
  Lokk jumps out of the hatch, and spots the newcomers, "Hey, who 
are you and what was it you were saying before?"
  Axis comes out behind Lokk, and lands on the ground behind Lokk.
